
0. Build Dockerfile and Github CICD - use example from my k8s project.
1. Create REDIS instance via Kubernetes
2. Capture screen for various VMs from docker container.
  2.1 Capture from Ubuntu
  2.2 Capture from Docker
  2.3 Capture from Windows
3. build api layer to handle read/writes to redis.
4. Build swagger API page for this.
5. send data to the API layer.

